column1: INTERNATIONAL SCHEDULED AIR TRANSPORT - Airline supplied data
Country is determined by where "same flight number" services Originate or Terminate

The true seat utilisation factors for airlines other than Australian Airlines, Qantas Airways, Emirates (for November 2011 onwards), China Airlines (for January 2014 onwards), Philippine Airlines (for December 2015 onwards), AirAsia X (for March 2016 onwards) and Singapore Airlines (for September 2016 onwards), that operate via Australia will most likely be higher than what is calculated using this data.
